        question: 'How does the Pradhan Mantri Suraksha Bima\nYojana (PMSBY) seek to provide social\nsecurity to economically vulnerable sections of\nIndia?\nI. By offering accidental death and disability\ncover at an annual premium of ₹20.\nII. By providing life insurance cover against\ndeath due to any cause, including natural\ndeath and critical illness, for all citizens\nabove the poverty line.\nIII. By targeting unbanked and unorganised\nsector workers through Jan Dhan accounts\nas the primary enrollment channel.\nSelect the correct answer using the code given\nbelow.',
