        question: 'Chairperson and other members of the\nNational Human Rights Commission of India\nare appointed by the President of India based\non the recommendation of a committee\nconsisting of which among the following\nmembers?\nI. Prime Minister\nII. Speaker of the House of the People\nIII. Leader of the Opposition in the House of\nthe People\nIV. Leader of the Opposition in the Council of\nStates\nV. Chairperson of the Council of States\nSelect the correct answer using the code given\nbelow.',
