        question: 'In the context of biofuels and alternative fuels,\nconsider the following pairs:\nFuel Feedstock used for\nproduction\nI. Bioethanol : Vegetable oils and\nanimal fats\nII. Biodiesel : Sugarcane and corn\nIII. Bio-CNG : Agricultural residues\nand organic waste\nHow many of the pairs given above are\ncorrectly matched?',
