        question: 'A recent scientific study has found that lakes\nMai Ndombe and Tumba are releasing ancient\ncarbon stored for thousands of years in\nsurrounding peatlands, raising fresh climate\nconcerns. In which of the following river\nbasins do these lakes lie?',
