        question: 'Consider the following statements regarding\nGreen Ammonia:\nI. Green ammonia is produced using\nhydrogen generated through electrolysis of\nwater powered by renewable energy\nsources.\nII. It can be used as fuel for engines such as\nlocomotives and shipping.\nIII. Combustion of ammonia produces only\nwater and hydrogen as by-products.\nWhich of the statements given above are\ncorrect?',
