        question: 'Consider the following:\nI. Black-footed Cat\nII. Fishing cat\nIII. Margay\nIV. Caracal\nV. Desert cat\nHow many of the above small cat species are\nfound in India?',
        options: { a: 'Only two', b: 'Only three', c: 'Only four', d: 'All five' },
