        question: 'Consider the following pairs:\nNeutrino Observatories Country\nI.Jiangmen Neutrino : Japan\nObservatory\nII.Karlsruhe Tritium : Germany\nNeutrino Observatory\nIII.IceCube Neutrino : India\nObservatory\nHow many pairs given above are correctly\nmatched?',
