        question: 'In the context of famous women in India,\nconsider the following pairs:\nWomen Popularly Known As\nI.Shakuntala : Human computer\nDevi\nII.Tessy Thomas : Rocket Woman of\nIndia\nIII. Ritu Karidhal : Missile Woman of\nSrivastava India\nWhich of the pairs given above is/are correctly\nmatched?',
